{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And ORT was able to really give them a skill that they used when they arrived in Israel and used it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war-- after liberation, I was involved with-- there's a European branch of Haganah, which was called B'richa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And B'richa's main-- main act was to take the people out of the camps and send them to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so there were many organizations that were working, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was Betar.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Betar was Likud.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Likud was the party of Begin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They put their name down on the list.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All they want to know-- was to go, leave, get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they put their name down on the first guy who came and put the list in front of them-- put your name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those who were with Betar never left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They weren't leaving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The ones with B'richa were leaving, because they were Labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Labor Party, of course, took care of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had enough boats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I did that once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I went up with a young man, by the name of [NON-ENGLISH] who was in Munich.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went up-- do you remember the story of the Exodus boat?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That the British took them to a German camp in Papendorf?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to Papendorf to get some of them out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so some of our guys were putting themselves in British uniforms as British MPs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the MPs were shifting guard, they were taking their place, and getting into the camp, and getting a-- a truck full of people, and go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went through the whole of Germany-- the French zone, the British zone, and finally, the last one was the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The American zone was the first.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
